race.comment: STEPHEN WITHERAP (8) recorded a 0.8 lengths win (18.13) in a NG last time at this track. Yet to taste defeat in two runs from this draw. Looks a leading chance on best. GRID GIRL (1) broke a string of placings finishing in the money four on end before a last start fifth (20.71) at Goulburn. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from five starts. Better than last start and can bounce back. CRIMSON DYNAMO (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (18.29) in a NG at this track. Solid record at the distance winning seven races. A big run wouldn't surprise. ALMOST (5) is not to be discarded.
